 unique combo system to your advantage and change the tide of the combat.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114380/extras/034f5bd379c9238da120f8d581befdfc.webp?t=1765613899\" width=500 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114380/extras/4ccab3f89694811192d06199116a06f4.poster.avif?t=1765613899\" width=672 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114380/extras/4ccab3f89694811192d06199116a06f4.webm?t=1765613899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114380/extras/4ccab3f89694811192d06199116a06f4.mp4?t=1765613899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Hundreds of items, helmets, armors and accessories to equip your party with.<br></li><li>Unlock permanent perks, some could even change how you play the game.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114380/extras/f054c1baf64d713241faa6fce0386deb.webp?t=1765613899\" width=500 height=60 /></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114380/extras/ddb2e0a6cb783deec82e2b7843f7fe7d.poster.avif?t=1765613899\" width=672 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114380/extras/ddb2e0a6cb783deec82e2b7843f7fe7d.webm?t=1765613899\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2114380/extras/ddb2e0a6cb783deec82e2b7843f7fe7d.mp4?t=1765613899\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>Over 30 skills. Every skill has its own skill tree. Define your very own build.<br></li><li>Enhance your companions with adventurer classes, along with the powerful ult skills. </li></ul>",
